<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4804060>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 4–8. Larva of Rhyacophila fasciata Hagen 1859. 4a–4c, head: 4a, dorsal; 4b, right lateral; 4c, frontoclypeus, dorsal. 5D, 5V, mandibles from last instar larval exuviae, left (l) and right (r): 5D, dorsal; 5V, ventral. 6a, 6b, prothorax: 6a, dorsal; 6b, left hemisclerite, left lateral. 7, dorsal sclerite of abdominal tergum IX. 8a–8c, details of anal prolegs: 8a, right anal claw, right lateral; 8b, detail of basolateral plate with sword process and basoventral hook, right lateral; 8c, detail of claw, right lateral. Scale bar: unlabelled = 1 mm; ● = 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4804060/files/figure.png" .

